{"tid":984732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子蒲吧被偷錢兼打傷 警拘兩男女","createTime":"2019-01-17T04:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T04:59:08.000Z","uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df337bbabf052aabd264174498da14e1401f1879","tid":984732,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"女子蒲吧被偷錢兼打傷 警拘兩男女<br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴諾士佛臺9號地下一間酒吧，凌晨3時53分，一名姓謝24歲女子與友人飲酒消遣，其間發覺手袋內1,000元被人偷走，懷疑是一名姓趙44歲女酒客所為，趙矢口否認，雙方發生爭執。<br />\n<br />\n其間，趙女姓黃（39歲）男朋友拳毆謝女。警方接報到場，經初步調查，黃男涉嫌普通襲擊被捕；而趙女則涉嫌企圖盜竊被捕，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進。謝女受傷，清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。據了解，謝女及兩名被捕人身上均有酒氣。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190117/large/1547672531_755e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190117%2Flarge%2F1547672531_755e.jpg&h=ad017190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方拘捕涉嫌盜竊女子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190117/59151899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F59151899&d=UvKuUuc4QvHjzgPyDvtmWzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=83656f8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F59151899&h=b9228ee6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190117/59151899</a>"},{"pid":"e800042d78d32865149e0e8540c5c08181fde689","tid":984732,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">趙女姓黃（39歲）</span>"},{"pid":"2e4ca93c5d12b25693c396ee0aface1bfd781302","tid":984732,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e800042d78d32865149e0e8540c5c08181fde689","tid":984732,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">趙女姓黃（39歲）</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475782a4de6a034166de09a5c42b1cce4b7fc085","tid":984732,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"差15年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}